Addressing Your Research Needs

Otis Chadley
Subjects:African American Studies, Anthropology, Family Science, Psychology, Sociology

Welcome!

This online course tutorial will assist students of SOCY 464: Military Sociology.  It will help you in locating print and electronic resources on your topic.  The tutorial covers military related topics on a national and international basis.  Also, the publication includes tips on how to prepare an annotated bibliography.   Always consult with your course instructor for specific requirements regarding your assignments.
